)/, '').split('@')[0]);\n            if (pNums.includes(mencNum)) {\n              // Retornar o ID principal do participante (o que a API do WhatsApp reconhece)\n              return p.id;\n            }\n          }\n          return mencId; // Fallback\n        };\n\n        var menc_sticker = (info.mentionedJid && info.mentionedJid.length > 0) ? normalizar(info.mentionedJid[0]) : normalizar(info.message?.stickerMessage?.contextInfo?.participant) || null;\n\n        var menc_prt = info.message?.extendedTextMessage?.contextInfo?.participant || info.message?.stickerMessage?.contextInfo?.participant || ''; menc_prt = normalizar(menc_prt);\n\n        var menc_jid2 = info.message?.extendedTextMessage?.contextInfo?.mentionedJid || info.message?.stickerMessage?.contextInfo?.mentionedJid || [];\n\n        if (menc_jid2?.length > 0) {\n          menc_jid2[0] = normalizar(menc_jid2[0]);\n        }\n\n        var menc_os2 = q.includes("@") ? (Array.isArray(menc_jid2) && menc_jid2.length > 0 ? menc_jid2[0] : menc_sticker || null) : menc_prt || menc_sticker;\n\n        var menc_jid = normalizar(menc_os2 || sender);\n        var sender_ou_n = q.includes("@") ? (menc_jid2?.[0] || menc_sticker) : (menc_prt || menc_sticker || sender);\n\n        var numClean = txt => txt.replace(/[()+\-\/\s]/g, '') + '@s.whatsapp.net';\n        var mrc_ou_numero = q.length > 6 && !q.includes('@') ? numClean(q) : normalizar(menc_prt || menc_sticker);\n\n        var marc_tds = q.includes('@') ? normalizar(menc_jid) : q.length > 6 && !q.includes('@') ? numClean(q) : normalizar(menc_prt || menc_sticker);\n\n        var menc_prt_nmr = q.length > 12 && !q.includes('@') ? numClean(q) : normalizar(menc_prt || menc_sticker);\n\n        ////////////////////////////////////////////\n\n        var isUrl = (url) => {\n          if (linkfy.find(url)[0]) return true\n          return false\n        }\n\n        //\n        var time2 = moment().tz('America/Sao_Paulo').format('HH:mm:ss');\n\n        if (time2 > "00:00:00" && time2 < "05:00:00") {\n          var tempo = 'Boa noite'\n          var tempo2 = 'ʙᴏᴀ ɴᴏɪᴛᴇ'\n        } if (time2 > "05:00:00" && time2 < "12:00:00") {\n          var tempo = 'Bom dia'\n          var tempo2 = 'ʙᴏᴍ ᴅɪᴀ'\n        } if (time2 > "12:00:00" && time2 < "18:00:00") {\n          var tempo = 'Boa tarde'\n          var tempo2 = 'ʙᴏᴀ ᴛᴀʀᴅᴇ'\n        } if (time2 > "18:00:00") {\n          var tempo = 'Boa noite'\n          var tempo2 = 'ʙᴏᴀ ɴᴏɪᴛᴇ'\n        }\n\n        if (!isCmd && info.key.fromMe) return\n        var reply = (text) => {\n          var messageOptions = {\n            text,\n            contextInfo: { ...gerarContextNewsletter(), mentionedJid: Array.from(senderAllIds) }\n          };\n          return corvo.sendMessage(from, messageOptions, {\n            quoted: selo\n          }).catch(error => {\n            console.error(error);\n          });\n        };\n        async function sendAudioMenu(from) {\n          var soundft = fs.readFileSync('./DADOS DO CORVO/data/media/audios/menu.mp3');\n          await corvo.sendMessage(from, {\n            audio: soundft,\n            mimetype: "audio/mpeg",\n            contextInfo: gerarContextNewsletter(),\n          }, { quoted: selo });\n        }\n        var NkChannelKk = gerarContextNewsletter();\n\n        async function sendUrlText(id, textCaption, title, desc, imageUrl, linkAcess, quotedThis) {\n          await corvo.sendMessage(id, { text: textCaption, contextInfo: { externalAdReply: { title: title, body: desc, thumbnail: await getBuffer(imageUrl), mediaType: 1, sourceUrl: linkAcess } } }, { contextInfo: { ...NkChannelKk } }, { quoted: quotedThis })\n        }\n\n        async function replyWithNewsletter(text, options = {}, quotedThis = info) {\n          await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: text, contextInfo: options }, { quoted: quotedThis })\n            .catch(async (error) => {\n              await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: mess.error() }, { quoted: selo });\n            });\n        }\n\n        async function replyWithReaction(text, options = {}, quotedThis = info) {\n          await corvo.sendMessage(from, options)\n          await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: text }, { quoted: quotedThis })\n            .catch(async (error) => {\n              await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: mess.error() }, { quoted: selo });\n            });\n        }\n\n        var sendSticker = async (ChatID, FileN, quotedThis) => {\n          await corvo.sendMessage(ChatID, { sticker: { url: FileN } }, { contextInfo: { ...NkChannelKk } }, { quoted: selo }\n          )\n            .catch(async (error) => {\n              await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: mess.error() }, { quoted: selo });\n            });\n        }\n\n        var sendImage = async (ChatID, FileN) => {\n          await corvo.sendMessage(ChatID, { image: { url: FileN } }, { contextInfo: { ...NkChannelKk } }, { quoted: selo }\n          ).catch(async (error) => {\n            await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: mess.error() }, { quoted: selo });\n          })\n        }\n\n        var sendText = async (ChatID, texto) => {\n          await corvo.sendMessage(ChatID, { text: texto }, { contextInfo: { ...NkChannelKk } }\n          ).catch(async (error) => {\n            await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: mess.error() }, { quoted: selo });\n          });\n        }\n\n\n        var sendMentions = async (local, teks) => {\n          memberr = []; vy = teks.includes('\n') ? teks.split('\n') : [teks]\n          for (vz of vy) {\n            for (zn of vz.split(' ')) {\n              if (zn.includes('@')) {\n                var numPart = zn.split('@')[1]?.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '');\n                if (numPart) { memberr.push(numPart + '@s.whatsapp.net'); memberr.push(numPart + '@lid'); }\n              }\n            }\n          };\n          await corvo.sendMessage(local, { text: teks.trim(), contextInfo: { ...NkChannelKk, mentionedJid: memberr } }, { quoted: selo }).catch(async (e) => {\n            await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: mess.error() }, { quoted: selo });\n          });\n        }\n\n        var mentions = async (teks = '', mb, id) => {\n          (id == null || id == undefined || id == false) ? await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: teks.trim(), mentions: mb }) : await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: teks.trim(), contextInfo: { ...NkChannelKk, mentionedJid: mb } }, { quoted: selo })\n        }\n\n        var mention = async (teks = '', ms = info) => {\n          memberr = []\n          vy = teks.includes('\n') ? teks.split('\n') : [teks]\n          for (vz of vy) {\n            for (zn of vz.split(' ')) {\n              if (zn.includes('@')) {\n                var numPart = zn.split('@')[1]?.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '');\n                if (numPart) { memberr.push(numPart + '@s.whatsapp.net'); memberr.push(numPart + '@lid'); }\n              }\n            }\n          }\n          await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: teks.trim(), contextInfo: { ...NkChannelKk, mentionedJid: memberr } }, { quoted: selo }).catch(async (e) => {\n            await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: mess.error() }, { quoted: selo });\n          });\n        }\n\n        var mentionSemQuoted = async (teks) => {\n          memberr = []\n          vy = teks.includes('\n') ? teks.split('\n') : [teks]\n          for (vz of vy) {\n            for (zn of vz.split(' ')) {\n              if (zn.includes('@')) {\n                var numPart = zn.split('@')[1]?.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '');\n                if (numPart) { memberr.push(numPart + '@s.whatsapp.net'); memberr.push(numPart + '@lid'); }\n              }\n            }\n          }\n          await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: teks.trim(), contextInfo: { ...NkChannelKk, mentionedJid: memberr } }, { quoted: selo }).catch(async (e) => {\n            await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: mess.error() }, { quoted: selo });\n          });\n        }\n\n        var mencionarIMG = async (teks = '', FileN, thisQuoted = info) => {\n          memberr = []\n          vy = teks.includes('\n') ? teks.split('\n') : [teks]\n          for (vz of vy) {\n            for (zn of vz.split(' ')) {\n              if (zn.includes('@')) {\n                var numPart = zn.split('@')[1]?.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '');\n                if (numPart) { memberr.push(numPart + '@s.whatsapp.net'); memberr.push(numPart + '@lid'); }\n              }\n            }\n          }\n          await corvo.sendMessage(from, { image: { url: FileN }, caption: teks.trim(), mentions: memberr }, { quoted: thisQuoted }).catch(async (error) => {\n            await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: mess.error() }, { quoted: selo });\n          });\n        }\n\n        // Helper: verificar se um JID (qualquer formato) é admin do grupo\n        function isJidAdmin(jid) {\n          if (!isGroup || !groupMetadata?.participants || !jid) return false;\n          var jidClean = (typeof jid === 'string' ? jid : '').replace(/:.*(?=@)/, '');\n          return groupMetadata.participants.some(p => {\n            if (p.admin !== 'admin' && p.admin !== 'superadmin') return false;\n            var pIds = [p.id, p.jid, p.lid, p.phoneNumber, p.participant]\n              .filter(Boolean)\n              .map(x => x.replace(/:.*(?=@)/, ''));\n            return pIds.includes(jidClean);\n          });\n        }\n\n        // Helper: verificar se um JID é o bot\n        function isJidBot(jid) {\n          if (!jid) return false;\n          var jidClean = (typeof jid === 'string' ? jid : '').replace(/:.*(?=@)/, '').split('@')[0];\n          var botNum = botNumber.split('@')[0];\n          var botLidNum = (corvo?.user?.lid || '').replace(/:.*(?=@)/, '').split('@')[0];\n          return jidClean === botNum || jidClean === botLidNum;\n        }\n\n        var reagir = async (idgp, emj) => {\n          await corvo.sendMessage(idgp, { react: { text: emj, key: info.key } });\n        }\n\n        var verificarN = async (sla) => {\n          var [result] = await corvo.onWhatsApp(sla)\n          if (result == undefined) {\n            reply("Este usuário não é existente no WhatsApp")\n          } else {\n            reply(`${sla} Número inserido é existente no WhatsApp com o id: ${result.jid}`)\n          }\n        }\n\n\n        if (isGroup && isBotGroupAdmins && !isGroupAdmins && !SoDono && !info.key.fromMe) {\n          if (menc_jid2?.length >= groupMembers.length - 1) {\n            await corvo.sendMessage(from, { text: mess.markingAllMember() }, { quoted: selo });\n            if (IS_DELETE) {\n              setTimeout(async () => {\n                await corvo.sendMessage(from, { delete: info.key });\n              }, 500);\n            }\n            corvo.groupParticipantsUpdate(from, [encontrarJidReal(sender)], "remove");\n          }\n        }\n\n        if (isAutofigu && isGroup) {\n          async function autofiguf() {\n            setTimeout(async () => {\n              if (budy.includes(`${prefix}sticker`) || budy.includes(`${prefix}s`) || budy.includes(`${prefix}stk`) || budy.includes(`${prefix}st`) || budy.includes(`${prefix}fsticker`) || budy.includes(`${prefix}f`) || budy.includes(`${prefix}fstiker`)) return\n              if (type == 'imageMessage') {\n                var pack = `${pushname}`\n                var author2 = `${pushname}`\n                owgi = await getFileBuffer(info.message.imageMessage, 'image')\n                var encmediaa = await sendImageAsSticker2(corvo, from, owgi, selo, { packname: pack, author: author2 })\n                DLT_FL(encmediaa)\n              }\n              if (type == 'videoMessage') {\n                if ((isMedia && info.message.videoMessage.seconds < 10)) {\n                  var pack = `${pushname}`\n                  var author2 = `${pushname}`\n                  owgi = await getFileBuffer(info.message.videoMessage, 'video')\n                  var encmedia = await sendVideoAsSticker2(corvo, from, owgi, selo, { packname: pack, author: author2 })\n                  DLT_FL(encmedia)\n                }\n              }\n            }, 1000)\n          }\n          autofiguf().catch((error) => {\n            console.log(error)\n          })\n        }\n        function msToTime(ms) {\n          var seg = Math.floor(ms / 1000)\n          var min = Math.floor(seg / 60)\n          var hr = Math.floor(min / 60)\n          var dia = Math.floor(hr / 24)\n          var ano = Math.floor(dia / 365)\n          seg %= 60\n          min %= 60\n          hr %= 24\n          dia %= 365\n          var partes = []\n          if (ano) partes.push(`${ano} ᴀɴᴏ${ano > 1 ? 'ꜱ' : ''}`)\n          if (dia) partes.push(`${dia} ᴅɪᴀ${dia > 1 ? 'ꜱ' : ''}`)\n          if (hr) partes.push(`${hr} ʜᴏʀᴀ${hr > 1 ? 'ꜱ' : ''}`)\n          if (min) partes.push(`${min} ᴍɪɴᴜᴛᴏ${min > 1 ? 'ꜱ' : ''}`)\n          if (seg) partes.push(`${seg} ꜱᴇɢᴜɴᴅᴏ${seg > 1 ? 'ꜱ' : ''}`)\n          return partes.length ? partes.join(', ').replace(/,([^,]*)$/, ' e$1') : 'ᴀɢᴏʀᴀ ʜᴀ ᴩᴏᴜᴄᴏ'\n        }\n\n        if (isGroup && dataGp[0].ausentes?.length > 0) {\n          var afkList = dataGp[0].ausentes;\n          if (menc_jid2?.length > 0) {\n            for (var m of menc_jid2) {\n              var afkUser = afkList.find(x => x.id === m);\n              if (afkUser) {\n                var tempo = msToTime(Date.now() - afkUser.hora);\n                await corvo.sendMessage(from, {\n                  text: mess.ausente(afkUser, tempo, m),\n                  mentions: [m],\n                  contextInfo: { ...NkChannelKk, mentionedJid: [m] }\n                }, { quoted: selo })\n              }\n            }\n          }\n          var eu_afk = afkList.find(x => x.id === sender);\n          if (eu_afk) {\n            var tempo = msToTime(Date.now() - eu_afk.hora);\n            dataGp[0].ausentes = afkList.filter(x => x.id !== sender);\n            setGp(dataGp);\n            await corvo.sendMessage(from, {\n              text: mess.on(sender, tempo),\n              mentions: [sender],\n              contextInfo: { ...NkChannelKk, mentionedJid: [sender] }\n            }, { quoted: selo })\n          }\n        }\n\n        if (!isVip && nescessario.cmd_vip.includes(command)) return reply(mess.onlyVipUser());\n\n        //BAN GRUPO & BOT OFF\n        if (isGroup && isCmd && isBanchat && !itsMe && !SoDono) { if (command && ['d','del','delete','deletar','apagar'].includes(command)) console.log('[DEL-BLOCK] Bloqueado por isBanchat'); return }\n\n        if (isGroup && isCmd && So_Adm && !SoDono && !itsMe && !isGroupAdmins) { if (command && ['d','del','delete','deletar','apagar'].includes(command)) console.log('[DEL-BLOCK] Bloqueado por So_Adm (soadm) - isGroupAdmins:', isGroupAdmins, 'SoDono:', SoDono, 'itsMe:', itsMe); return }\n\n        if (isBotoff && !itsMe && !SoDono) { if (command && ['d','del','delete','deletar','apagar'].includes(command)) console.log('[DEL-BLOCK] Bloqueado por isBotoff'); return }\n\n        //=======================================\\\n\n        var sendStickerFromUrl = async (to, url) => {\n          try {\n            var names = Date.now() / 10000;\n            var download = function (uri, filename, callback) {\n              request.head(uri, function (err, res, body) {\n                request(uri).pipe(fs.createWriteStream(filename)).on('close', callback);\n              });\n            };\n            download(url, './sticker' + names + '.png', async function () {\n              var filess = './sticker' + names + '.png'\n              var asw = './sticker' + names + '.webp'\n              exec(`ffmpeg -i ${filess} -vcodec libwebp -filter:v fps=fps=15 -lossless 1 -loop 0 -preset default -an -vsync 0 -s 800:800 ${asw}`, async (err) => {\n                var media = fs.readFileSync(asw)\n                await corvo.sendMessage(to, { sticker: media }, { sendEphemeral: true, contextInfo: { forwardingScore: 50, isForwarded: true }, quoted: selo }).catch(async (error) => {\n                  return reply(mess.error())\n                })\n                DLT_FL(filess)\n                DLT_FL(asw)\n              });\n            });\n          } catch {\n            return reply(mess.error())\n          }\n        }\n\n        //=========(isQuoted/consts)=============\\\n\n        var isImage = type == 'imageMessage'\n        var isVideo = type == 'videoMessage'\n        var isVisuU2 = type == 'viewOnceMessageV2'\n        var isAudio = type == 'audioMessage'\n        var isSticker = type == 'stickerMessage'\n        var isContact = type == 'contactMessage'\n        var isLocation = type == 'locationMessage'\n        var isProduct = type == 'productMessage'\n        var isMedia = (type === 'imageMessage' || type === 'videoMessage' || type === 'audioMessage' || type == "viewOnceMessage" || type == "viewOnceMessageV2")\n        typeMessage = body.substr(0, 50).replace(/\n/g, '')\n        if (isImage) typeMessage = "Image"\n        else if (isVideo) typeMessage = "Video"\n        else if (isAudio) typeMessage = "Audio"\n        else if (isSticker) typeMessage = "Sticker"\n        else if (isContact) typeMessage = "Contact"\n        else if (isLocation) typeMessage = "Location"\n        else if (isProduct) typeMessage = "Product"\n\n        var isQuotedMsg = type === 'extendedTextMessage' && content.includes('conversation')\n\n        var isQuotedMsg2 = type === 'extendedTextMessage' && content.includes('text')\n\n        var isQuotedImage = type === 'extendedTextMessage' && content.includes('imageMessage')\n\n        var isQuotedVisuU = type === 'extendedTextMessage' && content.includes('viewOnceMessage')\n\n        var isQuotedVisuU2 = type === 'extendedTextMessage' && content.includes('viewOnceMessageV2')\n\n        var isQuotedVideo = type === 'extendedTextMessage' && content.includes('videoMessage')\n\n        var isQuotedDocument = type === 'extendedTextMessage' && content.includes('documentMessage')\n\n        var isQuotedDocW = type === 'extendedTextMessage' && content.includes('documentWithCaptionMessage')\n\n        var isQuotedAudio = type === 'extendedTextMessage' && content.includes('audioMessage')\n\n        var isQuotedSticker = type === 'extendedTextMessage' && content.includes('stickerMessage')\n\n        var isQuotedContact = type === 'extendedTextMessage' && content.includes('contactMessage')\n\n        var isQuotedLocation = type === 'extendedTextMessage' && content.includes('locationMessage')\n\n        var isQuotedProduct = type === 'extendedTextMessage' && content.includes('productMessage')\n\n        // ANTI DDD - LISTA COMPLETA DE DDDs EXISTENTES NO BRASIL!\n        var arrayDDDs = [11, 12, 13, 14, 15, 16, 17, 18, 19, 21, 22, 24, 27, 28, 31, 32, 33, 34, 35, 37, 38, 41, 42, 43, 44, 45, 46, 47, 48, 49, 51, 53, 54, 55, 61, 62, 63, 64, 65, 66, 67, 68, 69, 71, 73, 74, 75, 77, 79, 81, 82, 83, 84, 85, 86, 87, 88, 89, 91, 93, 94, 95, 96, 97, 98, 99];\n\n        //////BLOCK CMD///////\n        budy = body.toLowerCase().normalize('NFD').replace(/[\u0300-\u036f]/g, "");\n\n        if (isGroup) {\n          var checar = getComandos(from)\n          if (checar === undefined) addComandosId(from)\n        }\n        if (isGroup && isCmd && !SoDono && !isnit && getComandoBlock(from).includes(command)) return reply('O comando foi bloqueado, entre em contato com a administração.')\n\n        ///BLOCK CMD GLOBAL///\n        ///(CRÉDITOS AO @VictorGabriel)///\n        if (command && isblockCmdG.includes(command) && !SoDono) return reply('Olá, o comando está bloqueado para *uso global*, ou seja, todos os usuários estão impossibilitados de usar ele.\n–\n• Entre em contato com meu proprietário para saber o motivo.')\n\n        ////FIMMMMMMMMM/////            \n\n        ///// FIMMMMMMMMMMMMM /////\n\n        var dattofc = moment.tz('America/Sao_Paulo').format('DD/MM/YYYY')\n        var hourofc = moment.tz('America/Sao_Paulo').format('HH:mm:ss')\n\n        var MessageType = type == 'audioMessage' ? 'Áudio' : type == 'stickerMessage' ? 'Figurinha' : type == 'imageMessage' ? 'Imagem' : type == 'videoMessage' ? 'Vídeo' : type == 'documentMessage' ? 'Documento' : type == 'pollCreationMessage' ? 'Enquete' : type == 'contactMessage' ? 'Contato' : type == 'locationMessage' ? 'Localização' : info.message?.reactionMessage?.text ? `Reação '${info.message.reactionMessage.text}'` : `${prefix + command}`;\n\n        //===============INTERAÇÃO NO TERMUX=====================\n        if (isConsole) {\n          var chalk = require('chalk');\n          var user = chalk.hex('#D500F9').bold(pushname?.toUpperCase() || 'DESCONHECIDO');\n          var number = chalk.yellowBright(addNumberMais(sender));\n          var chatType = isGroup ? 'GRUPO' : 'PRIVADO';\n          var groupInfo = isGroup ? `(${groupName})` : '(Privado)';\n          var typeMap = { isCmd: ['COMANDO', chalk.cyanBright(`${prefix}${command}`)], isImage: ['MÍDIA', '🖼️ IMAGEM'], isVideo: ['MÍDIA', '🎞️ VÍDEO'], isAudio: ['MÍDIA', '🎧 ÁUDIO'], isSticker: ['MÍDIA', '🔖 FIGURINHA'], isLocation: ['MÍDIA', '📍 LOCALIZAÇÃO'], isProduct: ['MÍDIA', '🛒 CATÁLOGO'], isQuotedDocument: ['MÍDIA', '📄 DOCUMENTO'], isQuotedContact: ['MÍDIA', '👤 CONTATO'], isPoll: ['MÍDIA', '📊 ENQUETE'] };\n          var detectedType = Object.entries({\n            isCmd, isImage, isVideo, isAudio, isSticker, isLocation, isProduct, isQuotedDocument, isQuotedContact, isPoll: q?.includes('###')\n          }).find(([_, val]) => val);\n          var [msgType, msgContent] = detectedType ? [chalk.redBright(typeMap[detectedType[0]][0]), typeMap[detectedType[0]][1]] : [chalk.whiteBright('MENSAGEM'), (q || '').slice(0, 25) + ((q || '').length > 25 ? '...' : '')];\n          process.nextTick(() => {\n            console.log(chalk.hex('#7B1FA2')(`╭──. ݁ ⛧ ₊ ⊹ 🦇. ݁ ˖ ♱ . ݁──╮\n | ⸸ ${isGroup ? 'MENSAGEM NO GRUPO' : 'MENSAGEM NO PRIVADO'}\n╰──. ݁ ⛧ ₊ ⊹ 🦇. ݁ ˖ ♱ . ݁──╯\n╭──. ݁ ⛧ ₊ ⊹ 🦇. ݁ ˖ ♱ . ݁──╮\n| ⸸ USUÁRIO: ${user}\n| ⸸ NÚMERO: ${number}\n| ⸸ CHAT: ${chatType} ${groupInfo}\n| ⸸ TIPO: ${ms